      "writtenOn": "2016-10-11T18:21:55Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "why?\nif it\u0027s for a null-termination, I\u0027d prefer to make it conditional:\nstd::string str;\nif (string[string.size()] !\u003d 0 {\n    str \u003d string;\n    string \u003d str;\n}\n\n... with a corresponding comment about NULL-termination",
